PERSONA:1 — SOC Analyst           (Written by:Tejas Sonawane)
Name: Alex Müller
Age: 29
Background: Works as a Security Operations Center (SOC) analyst in a mid-sized company in Berlin. Handles daily monitoring of alerts and incident investigation.
Technical Skill Level: High (familiar with SIEM tools, logs, networking, basic scripting)
Alex spends most of the day reviewing alerts generated by SIEM systems and deciding which ones are real threats. He often deals with alert fatigue and wants faster ways to understand what’s happening without digging through raw logs. He would use your system to quickly identify high-risk incidents and understand attack patterns through visual relationships. He values automation but still wants control over decisions. He prefers tools that reduce noise and give clear explanations. Time efficiency and clarity are critical for him.

Persona 2 — Security Engineer       (Written by: BHARADWAZ CIRASANAGANDLA)
Name: Priya Sharma
Age: 34
Background: Cybersecurity engineer responsible for deploying and maintaining SIEM systems like Wazuh. Works with infrastructure, rules, and  integrations.
