Persona 3 — Cybersecurity Student              (Written by: Kiran Doddapaneni)
Name: Daniel Weber
Age: 22
Background: Computer science student learning cybersecurity concepts and working on projects. Limited real-world experience but strong interest in SIEM and threat detection.
